# Project index

Before searching or walking the repo, read `AGENTS.md` at the project root.

- Use its feature → file map to open only the relevant Screen / ViewModel / repository / API paths.
- Do not scan `.git`, `.gradle`, `.idea`, `**/build`, or `app/production` / release artifacts.
- When you add a screen, repository, or module, update `AGENTS.md`.
